{"type":"message","id":"339abca9","parentId":"b0cb3135","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:33:01.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the tool. It's a multi-search-engine skill that uses web_fetch to search across 10 different search engines. The user wants me to search for information about our work positions (大客户代办虾 etc.) and then learn, understand, and remember it.\n\nLet me search for relevant information about these roles - particularly about key account processing, proxy services for big clients, etc. Let me also check what the team does based on the context I have.\n\nThe team is a \"shrimp\" (虾) themed organization with various roles:\n- 0: General Manager\n\n\n- 1: Brand Display\n- 2: Lead Generation\n- 3: Short Video\n- 3+: Private Domain Operations\n- 4A: Standard Sales\n- 4B: Key Account Sales\n- 5A: Standard Processing\n- 5B: Key Account Processor (me)\n- 6: After-sales Maintenance\n- 7: Data Analysis\n- 8: All-round Support\n\nSo this is an agency specializing in qualification proxy services for key accounts, leveraging short video marketing and lead generation strategies. I should now search for industry-specific information about key account management and qualification services to provide more targeted insights.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来用这个多搜索引擎，围绕我们虾兵团队的工作职位做全面搜索学习。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a20f596bb81d4e76b0d56db4","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=大客户销售+资质代办+工作流程+SOP","maxChars":8000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d0dec3ac29024f5aad60eff7","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://cn.bing.com/search?q=大客户项目管理+执行地图+风险管控&ensearch=0","maxChars":8000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dbf6a8d3e4f2400d8f03829e","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.so.com/s?q=代办资质+大客户交付+零退回零延误","maxChars":8000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c546b5d476e4445bb5ffaa3c","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://s